Sentencas: The acceptor-doped BaCeO3-BaZrO3 solid solution shows a good compromise between conductivity and chemical stability.
Titulo: Synthesis and characterization of BaZr0.3Ce0.5Y0.2-xYbxO3-δ proton conductor for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Y and/or Yb doped BaCeO3-BaZrO3 solid solution BaZr0.3Ce0.5Y0.2-xYbxO3-delta (x = 0, 0.05, 0.1, 0.15, 0.2) powders are synthesized via a typical citrate-nitrate combustion method in this work.
Titulo: Synthesis and characterization of BaZr0.3Ce0.5Y0.2-xYbxO3-δ proton conductor for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The crystal structure and electrical conductivity of BaZr0.3Ce0.5Y0.2-xYbxO3-delta are investigated.
Titulo: Synthesis and characterization of BaZr0.3Ce0.5Y0.2-xYbxO3-δ proton conductor for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The XRD results reveal all the powders possess orthorhombic perovskite structure.
Titulo: Synthesis and characterization of BaZr0.3Ce0.5Y0.2-xYbxO3-δ proton conductor for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The electrical conductivity decreases monotonously with increasing the proportion of Yb, and BaZr0.3Ce0.5Y0.2O3-delta exhibits the highest electrical conductivity.
Titulo: Synthesis and characterization of BaZr0.3Ce0.5Y0.2-xYbxO3-δ proton conductor for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Single cells with BaZr0.3Ce0.5Y0.2O3-delta a as the electrolyte are fabricated and tested, and the cell outputs excellent power density and stability.
Titulo: Synthesis and characterization of BaZr0.3Ce0.5Y0.2-xYbxO3-δ proton conductor for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The peak power density of the cell reaches as high as 513 and 396 mW cm(-2) at 650 and 600 degrees C, suggesting that BaZr0.3Ce0.5Y0.2O3-delta-based fuel cells are promising solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs) working at low temperatures.
Titulo: Synthesis and characterization of BaZr0.3Ce0.5Y0.2-xYbxO3-δ proton conductor for solid oxide fuel cells
